</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"Global"</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">outer</span><span class="p">():</span>
